## 12. Running alongside TesNet on the same ProBook

| | TesNet | AkwaabaFit |
|---|--------|------------|
| **Path** | `/var/www/MiniISP-Landing-page/TesNet` | `/var/www/AkwaabaFitAIProject/Backend` |
| **Database** | `tesnet` | `akwaabafit` |
| **Apache vhost** | `tesnet.conf` → `192.168.88.2` | `akwaabafit.conf` → `api.YOUR-DOMAIN.com` |
| **Public URL** | Cloudflare HTTPS (`portal.yourdomain.com`) | Cloudflare HTTPS (`api.YOUR-DOMAIN.com`) |
| **Paystack webhook** | `https://portal.yourdomain.com/portal/payments/webhook` | `https://api.YOUR-DOMAIN.com/api/webhook/paystack` |
| **FreeRADIUS** | Yes (TesNet only) | No |

Both apps can share **one Cloudflare tunnel** with two hostnames — see TesNet [`docs/CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL.md`](../TesNet/docs/CLOUDFLARE_TUNNEL.md).

