## 14. Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| `500` on all pages | `storage/` permissions; `php artisan config:clear`; read `storage/logs/laravel.log` |
| `SQLSTATE` connection error | Check `.env` `DB_*`; database exists; user granted |
| `Vite manifest not found` | Run `npm install && npm run build` on server |
| Mobile “network error” | Use HTTPS production URL, not LAN IP, on physical phones |
| Paystack paid, no session update | Webhook URL must be HTTPS; check `laravel.log` and Paystack webhook logs |
| Push not working | FCM JSON path; queue worker running |
| Cloudflare 502 | Apache down; wrong `httpHostHeader`; check `cloudflared` logs |
| Images 404 | `php artisan storage:link` |
| After `.env` change | `php artisan config:clear` and restart queue |

**Useful commands (ProBook):**

```bash
sudo systemctl status apache2 mariadb akwaabafit-queue cloudflared
sudo tail -f /var/www/AkwaabaFitAIProject/Backend/storage/logs/laravel.log
php artisan test
```

